data.text:
I noticed that a future connection finder will be race car drivers (the date for this is not certain because Motown was shifted into the schedule). I went looking for a Dutch driver and found Adrian Paulen. I made a very basic profile for him but I thought this might be a good profile for our project to try to connect and improve.

Two other deceased race car drivers are Dries van der Lof and Jan Flinterman. They were both born in 1919 so I don't know if any records are open for them
